title: Akhaijwng akhai homnanwi
lyrics:
Akhaijwng akhai homnanwi
Aganjwng agan surnanwi -2
Fwidwng jwng, beao boibw, rongza-rongza
(A)
Fwi jwng gwsw khousewi
Fwi jwng jiu mwnsewi -2
Dhwrwm guruni fwrwngnaikhou gwsw hwni
(B)
Lwrbang fwthainaikhou
Fwgwmfwi Phwrbuniao -2
Gwsw-gwrbwni, gajri mani, siman lani
